Lazard Recommends U.K. Government Sell Tote Bookmaker, FT Says

-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 
2011-04-09T08:31:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/lazard-recommends-u-k-government-sell-tote-bookmaker-ft-says.html
Lazard Ltd. has recommended to the
U.K. government that it should proceed with the sale of state-
owned bookmaker, the Tote, to Betfred Ltd., the Financial Times
 reported  without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
